<script>
    export default {
        methods:{
            getArticles(){
                var Urlbase = "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/articles/"
                return fetch(Urlbase,
                {
                    method: "GET",
                    headers:{
                        'Content-Type': 'application/json'
                    },
                    //body: JSON.stringify({id:3})
                })
                .then(res => res.json())
                .then(res =>{
                    let response = res 
                    console.log(response)
                    return response
                })
                .catch(error => console.log('error fetch',error))
            }
        }
    }
</script>
